{"parse":{"title":"tea plant","pageid":210752,"redirects":[],"wikitext":"==English==\n{{wikispecies|Camellia sinensis}}\n[[File:Tea Bud.jpg|thumb|right|Tea plant bud.]]\n\n===Pronunciation===\n* {{audio|en|LL-Q1860 (eng)-Flame, not lame-teaplant.wav|a=US}}\n\n===Noun===\n{{en-noun}}\n\n# The bush {{taxfmt|Camellia sinensis|species}}, the leaves of which are picked, dried and used to make the beverage [[tea]].\n#: {{cot|en|tea shrub}}\n\n====Translations====\n{{trans-top|''Camellia sinensis''}}\n* Catalan: {{t+|ca|te|m}}, {{t|ca|planta del te|f}}\n* Chinese:\n*: Mandarin: {{t+|cmn|茶樹|tr=cháshù}}\n* Czech: {{t+|cs|čajovník|m}}\n* Dutch: {{t+|nl|theestruik|m}}\n* Estonian: {{t|et|teepõõsas}}\n* Finnish: {{t+|fi|teepensas}}\n* French: {{t+|fr|théier|m}}\n* Galician: {{t|gl|planta do té}}\n* German: {{t+|de|Teepflanze|f}}\n* Italian: {{t|it|pianta del tè|f}}\n* Japanese: {{t+|ja|茶の木|tr=cha no ki}}\n* Kikuyu: {{t|ki|icani|c5}}\n* Polish: {{t+|pl|herbata|f}}\n* Portuguese: {{t+|pt|chá|m}}\n* Romanian: {{t+|ro|ceai|m}}\n* Russian: {{t+|ru|чай|m}}, {{t+|ru|ча́йный куст|m}}\n* Shan: {{t+|shn|ၼဵင်ႈ}}, {{t+|shn|ယိုဝ်ႉ}}\n* Sikkimese: {{t|sip|ཇ་ཞིང}}\n* Spanish: {{t|es|planta de té|f}}\n* Swahili: {{t+|sw|mchai}}\n* Welsh: {{t|cy|coeden de|f}}\n* Yakut: {{t|sah|чэй ыарҕата}}\n{{trans-bottom}}\n\n===Further reading===\n* {{pedia}}\n\n===Anagrams===\n* {{anagrams|en|a=aaelnptt|pantalet}}\n\n{{c|en|Ericales order plants|Tea}}"}}